    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "={{ $json.textInput }}",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "You are an expert intent classification AI for a WhatsApp chatbot serving a jewelry business.\n\nYour task is to analyze the user's message and classify it into one of these intent categories:\n\n1. suggestion - User is providing suggestions or ideas for improvement\n2. query - User is asking a general question about products, services, or processes\n3. support - User needs technical help or assistance with an issue\n4. review - User is providing feedback or a review about a product/service\n5. information - User is requesting specific information (catalog, details, specifications)\n6. feedback - General feedback about experience or service\n7. greeting - User is greeting or starting a conversation (hi, hello, etc.)\n8. model_shot_required - User is requesting or inquiring about professional model photography services\n9. gemstone_shot_required - User is requesting or inquiring about gemstone/product photography services\n10. pricing_cost - User is asking about prices, costs, or quotes\n11. credits_needed - User is inquiring about credits, payment, or account balance\n12. unknown - Message intent is unclear or doesn't fit any category\n\nAnalyze the message carefully and provide:\n- The most appropriate intent type\n- Confidence score (0-100)\n- Brief summary of the message\n- Reasoning for your classification"
        }
      },
      "id": "fab58275-d8a1-4c89-8ba0-0e088fb5503b",
      "name": "Text Intent Classification Agent",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3.1,
      "position": [
        816,
        624
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Text: {{ $json.textInput }}\n\nImage URL: {{ $json.imageUrl }}",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "You are an expert classification AI for a WhatsApp chatbot serving a jewelry business. You analyze both text messages and images together.\n\nYour task is to:\n1. Classify the TEXT INTENT into one of these categories:\n   - suggestion, query, support, review, information, feedback, greeting\n   - model_shot_required, gemstone_shot_required, pricing_cost, credits_needed, unknown\n\n2. Classify the IMAGE TYPE into one of these categories:\n   - professional_model_shot (model wearing jewelry)\n   - product_jewelry_gemstone (isolated product photography)\n   - other (anything else)\n\nAnalyze both the text and image together, as they provide context for each other. For example:\n- A message saying \"Can you shoot this?\" with a gemstone image = gemstone_shot_required intent\n- A greeting with a product image might indicate interest in that product\n\nProvide:\n- Intent type from the text\n- Image type from the image\n- Confidence score (0-100)\n- Text summary\n- Image description\n- Reasoning explaining how text and image relate"
        }
      },
